        "subject": "LU-19449 tests: survive sysfs leftovers in test cleanup",
        "message": "LU-19449 tests: survive sysfs leftovers in test cleanup\n\nAfter a client is unmounted, it can take a little bit of time to clean\nall sysfs entries up. So allow extra time before carrying on in\nremount_client_normally(). And just ignore -ENOENT when accessing\nfiles under sysfs in test cleanup phase.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nTest-Parameters: testgroup=review-dne-part-2\nTest-Parameters: testgroup=review-dne-selinux-ssk-part-2\nSigned-off-by: Sebastien Buisson <sbuisson@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Ida29cebfbf836040895162ee2025d4b967edaf6f\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/63135\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Chakshu Kansal <ckansal@ddn.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
